    Performance: 10.4ms (100B) → 66.7ms (200B)

STEP 3 — Asymmetric key encryption (key management):
    EncryptedKey = RSA-2048-OAEP-Encrypt(AES_Key, RSA_PublicKey)

STEP 4 — Bundle:
    Bundle = { EncryptedContent || EncryptedKey || IV }

STEP 5 — Distributed storage:
    CID = IPFS.add(Bundle)            // CID = SHA-256(Bundle) — immutable
    CID format: 46-char base58 (e.g., QmXk2fCn...)

STEP 6 — Blockchain anchoring:
    storePaper(paperId, CID, unlockTime)
    Emits: PaperStored(paperId, CID, unlockTime)
